lead_paragraph: Striker Benik Afobe says he will have nothing to prove on Sunday when Bournemouth entertain title-chasing Arsenal, his former club, in the Premier League.

headline.print_headline: I've Nothing to Prove to Arsenal, Says Bournemouth's Afobe
